/span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u65319e57\" id=\"u65319e57\"> 函数。如下面的公式返回任意两个整数之间的随机数，结果保留 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u0e3bcba1\" id=\"u0e3bcba1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u31094e5b\" id=\"u31094e5b\">1</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u40244a48\" id=\"u40244a48\"> 位小数：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub1756469\" id=\"ub1756469\"><br></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22Math.round((Math.random()%20*%20(max%20-%20min)%20%2B%20min)%20*%2010)%20%2F%2010%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22881d6021%22%7D\"></card>",
